PIConfiguration

PIConfiguration.Rd

An object storing configuration for the parameter identification

Super class

ospsuite.utils::Printable -> PIConfiguration

Active bindings

simulateSteadyState

Boolean representing whether the simulation should be brought to a steady-state first

steadyStateTime

Time in minutes to simulate if simulating steady-state. May be NULL

printIterationFeedback

Boolean. If TRUE, the output of the residuals calculation will be printed after each iteration. Default is FALSE
